  "title": "Project & Technical Sales Engineer | Kaki Bukit | 5 Days | Up To $7K + Bonus - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Project & Technical Sales Engineer</strong><br /><strong>Salary: </strong>$3600 - $7000 + Bonus<br /><strong>Working Days: </strong>Monday to Friday (9am - 6pm)<br /><strong>Working Location: </strong>Kaki Bukit </p><p><strong>Responsibilities & Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Autocad Drawings and project documentation</li><li>Project administration and scheduling</li><li>Technical Sales proposal and clarifications with customers</li><li>Project engineering and design</li><li>Hands-on product integration , troubleshooting, testing, etc. </li><li>Site Services on board vessel (local & overseas)</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Possess Electrical Engineering educational qualification</li><li>Relevant working experience in Engineering & onboard vessel site services. </li><li>Knowledge of PAGA, CCTV, PABX, Fire Alarm Systems, Fire & Gas systems, Helideck lightings systems, Weather Monitoring systems, Aids to Navigation systems, Instruments, added advantage.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
